Open data repositories
UC Irvine Machine Learning Repository: http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/ (Interested in the Bank Marketing dataset)
Kaggle Data Sets: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets (Useful search feature to find datasets of interest)

Pages that list open data repositories
Wikipedia's list of Machine Learning datasets: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_datasets_for_machine-learning_research (organized by subject and type of data)
Quora: https://www.quora.com/Where-can-I-find-large-datasets-open-to-the-public
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/datasets/
